description:
Super-light and moisture-wicking, this short sleeved tee uses Capilene® Cool Lightweight fabric to keep you dry during high-exertion activities. The Polygiene® antimicrobial treatment resists odour buildup so you can wear it more and wash it less.Classic Navy and Light Violet Blue colours are made with 77gsm 100% polyester fabric (37% recycled content).Peach Sherbet colour is made with 65gsm 100% recycled polyester fabric.Fabric wicks moisture from your skin to keep you comfortable.Polygiene® odour-management treatment keeps you smelling fresh.Set-in sleeves allow unrestricted movement.

